### next entry ###
A Wiki is the easiest possibility of collaborative writing on the internet.

There are much better descriptions of what a wiki is out there. For example you could visit the [http://c2.com/cgi/wiki father of the wikis] or the famous [http://www.wikipedia.org/ wikipedia]. Other popular examples are [http://www.usemod.com/cgi-bin/mb.pl meatball] and [http://www.infoanarchy.org/wiki/ InfoAnarchy].

The inventor of wiki is [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ward_Cunningham Ward Cunningham].
